Files
slist.c
implementation of a double linked list
class-----------------------------------

slist.c________________________________
structs------------
dbllist_node represent node
dbllist represent list
functions-------------------------------
dbllist_init _ start the list
dbllist_destroy _ free the lise
dbllist_append _ add to end  "node"
dbllist_prepend _ add ro start "node"
dbllist_remove _ remove node

pattern-matching.c____________________________
implementation of the  algoritm
structs -----------
pm_labeled_edge represent the arrow
pm_state  represent the node
pm_match  represent the match
pm represent tree
functions-------------------------------
pm_init _ start  the tree
pm_addstring _ add string to the tree
pm_makeFSM _ make the fail path
pm_goto_set _ make link between node "arrow"
pm_goto_get _ find link with lable
pm_fsm_search _ find the matchs
pm_destroy _ free the tree nods
=====================================   Input   =====================================
the Patterns Set by the function pm_addstring
the txet by function pm_fsm_search
====================================   Output   =====================================
the dbllist made from pm_match that represent the match in the text
